        "Description": "The &apos;Glazer Pandemic&apos; has began to swarm the globe, with thousands of individuals (primarily women) beginning to glaze the notorious slop farmer Kitchener Smith-Howell. \r\rWe&apos;ve managed to locate three glazers in the town of Sapienza: Federica Basadonne, Claudia Musella, and Lisa Almestoy.\r\rGood luck 47, and be careful, as these glazers are known to be rabid.",
